public class PercentageBigDecimalTextField
extends org.apache.wicket.markup.html.form.TextField<BigDecimal>

A TextField for BigDecimal percentage values. It is appropriate for percentage values with larger than four fraction digits.
It has a RangeValidator that guarantees that the percentage is not grater than a hundred and is equal or greater than zero. Note: Use this when you need High Precision.
